ip|website=uselectionatlas.org}}</ref>\n|- bgcolor=lightgrey\n! Year\n! [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n! [[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n! [[Third Party (United States)|Third parties]]\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[2016 United States presidential election|2016]]'''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''75.5%''' ''10,775''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|21.6% ''3,080''\n|  style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|3.0% ''422''\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[2012 United States presidential election|2012]]'''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''72.9%''' ''10,014''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|25.4% ''3,484''\n|  style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|1.7% ''236''\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[2008 United States presidential election|2008]]'''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''68.7%''' ''9,278''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|29.1% ''3,923''\n|  style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|2.2% ''300''\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[2004 United States presidential election|2004]]'''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''61.9%''' ''8,055''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|36.5% ''4,745''\n|  style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|1.6% ''207''\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[2000 United States presidential election|2000]]'''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''55.4%''' ''6,945''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|41.1% ''5,162''\n|  style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|3.5% ''439''\n|-\n|  style=\"text-al