ting the Keynesian Revolution|publisher=Routledge|year=2013|isbn=978-0-203-07752-8|lastauthoramp=y}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|first1=Nicholas|last1=Crafts|author1-link=Nicholas Crafts|first2=Peter|last2=Fearon|author2-link=|title=The Great Depression of the 1930s: Lessons for Today|publisher=[[Oxford University Press]], USA|year=2013|isbn=978-0-199-66318-7|lastauthoramp=y}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|first1=R.J.|last1=Crampton|author1-link=|title=A Short History of Modern Bulgaria|publisher=Cambridge University Press|year=1987|isbn=978-0-521-25340-6|lastauthoramp=y|url=https://archive.org/details/shorthistoryofmo00cram}}\n*{{Cite book|ref=harv|first1=Norman|last1=Davies|author1-link=Norman Davies|title=Europe at War 1939\u20131945: No Simple Victory|publisher=Pan Books|year=2007|isbn=978-033035-212-3|lastauthoramp=y|title-link=Europe at War 1939\u20131945: No Simple Victory}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.gresham.ac.uk/lectures-and-events/hitler-and-the-origins-of-the-war-1919-1939|ref=harv|last=Evans|first=Richard|author-link=Richard J. Evans|title=Hitler and the origins of the war, 1919\u20131939|publisher=[[Gresham College]]|year=2008|accessdate=27 April 2014}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|first=Charles H.|last=Feinstein|authorlink=Charles Feinstein|title=Banking, Currency, and Finance in Europe between the Wars|year=1995|publisher=Oxford University Press, USA|isbn=978-0-198-28803-9}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|first=Gerald D.|last=Feldman|authorlink=Gerald Feldman|title=The Great Disorder: Politics, Economics, and Society in the German Inflation 1914\u20131924|year=1997|origyear=1996|publisher=Oxford University Press, Inc|isbn=978-0-195-10114-0}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|first=Niall|last=Ferguson|authorlink=Niall Ferguson|title=The Pity of War: Explaining World War I|year=1998|publisher=[[Allen Lane]]|isbn=978-0-713-99246-5}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|first1=J.A.S|last1=Grenville|author1-link=John Grenville|first2=Bernard|last2=Wasserstein|author2-link=Bernard Wasserstein|title=